  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to SQLite</title>

    <para>
      The <application>SQLite</application> package is a software library that
      implements a self-contained, serverless, zero-configuration, transactional
      SQL database engine.
    </para>

    &lfs124_checked;

